<br>
A good guide to go for on questing ( as an enchanter i quest a LOT, and many times MQ for others ), is this.<br>
<br>
If you are not sure you have the faction to do a particular quest, TALK to the npc.<br>
<br>
Go thru the ENTIRE dialog, up to the point where he / she asks you for the items you are about to turn in.  I have never, ever seen an NPC actually ask me for the items and not return the piece i was questing for ( well ok it happens if they are bugged, but very rarely ).<br>
<br>
Many people are in such a rush to get their items, they just read who they are supposed to turn things into off a spoiler site and just hand in.  Never do this.  ALWAYS talk to the npc, even if you have quested with him before.  If they dont &quot;give&quot; you the quest, 99 percent of the time, you will NOT get the reward.<br>
<br>
